title: Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra 5G Smartphone with Galaxy AI (Titanium Gray, 12GB RAM, 512GB Storage), Titanium Frame, Snapdragon 8 Elite, 200 MP Camera with ProVisual Engine and 5000mAh Battery
description:
GALAXY AI - Ring in the next era of mobile AI with an AI companion who's one step ahead of your every need. Just let natural conversation guide the way to checking off everyday tasks with ease. Seamlessly complete your tasks without having to switch between various apps. Simply press and hold the side button to access Google Gemini for help.
GEMINI LIVE â€“ Go live, get answers. Have free-flowing conversation with Gemini Live to brainstorm ideas or prepare for presentations by attaching images and getting real-time responses that adapt to your conversation style.
NOW BRIEF - Get personalized briefings throughout the day from the all-new Now Brief. Start your morning with a run-down of the day ahead, such as checking your latest Energy Score and reminders of a busy schedule.
EPIC SHOTS, NO EFFORT - The sharpest details from Wide to Tele and even Ultra Wide. From Ultra Wide shots to the Telephoto camera, photos are clear and vivid at any angle. AI enhanced ProVisual Engine with the 200 MP Camera improves colour and details for next-level clarity.
SNAPDRAGON 8 ELITE FOR GALAXY - Introducing our most powerful processor, customised for Galaxy. With improved real-time ray tracing and Vulkan optimization, dive deep into the action with ultra-smooth gameplay thanks to Snapdragon 8 Elite Mobile Platform for Galaxy.
